1399
01:41:20,548 --> 01:41:21,798
Droga!

1400
01:41:23,590 --> 01:41:24,465
Droga!

1401
01:41:35,590 --> 01:41:37,715
Boa noite!

1402
01:42:06,790 --> 01:42:09,165
Direto do Dep. de Choque.

1403
01:42:09,248 --> 01:42:10,915
